The '''Decimator cannon''' was a deployable heavy weapon employed by the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]]. Its all-terrain [[tread]]s could transform into firm stabilizing feet. During the [[Battle for Alaris Prime]],<ref name="GB" /> between [[39 BBY/Legends|39 BBY]] and [[36 BBY/Legends|36 BBY]],<ref name="NEC">''[[The New Essential Chronology]]''</ref> [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] informed his Wookiee allies that they could construct Decimator cannons at their newly built [[Fortress/Legends|fortress]].<ref name="GB" />

